{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775895027862,"sessionID":"ses_28468ce19ffebZjIwGuVArSMoW","part":{"id":"prt_d7b979643001oIzwcm8ft9J9wm","messageID":"msg_d7b9781c2001gPlQF8DBcLt5vM","sessionID":"ses_28468ce19ffebZjIwGuVArSMoW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-019 Design: CLI Binary Entry Points\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: **AR ID:** AR-019  \n6: **Module:** `cmd`  \n7: **Language:** Go  \n8: **Size:** M (Medium)\n9: \n10: This module provides the CLI binary entry points for the 4 core AgentCube components. Each binary provides a standalone executable that initializes its respective service with proper configuration, dependency wiring, and graceful shutdown handling.\n11: \n12: ### Components\n13: \n14: | Binary | Purpose | Package Dependency |\n15: |--------|---------|-------------------|\n16: | `agentd` | Idle cleanup controller for AgentRuntime resources | `pkg/agentd` |\n17: | `router` | HTTP session routing proxy with JWT authentication | `pkg/router` |\n18: | `workload-manager` | Sandbox orchestration controller with CRD management | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n19: | `picod` | Sandbox daemon for code execution inside sandbox pods | `pkg/picod` |\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: ## Architecture\n24: \n25: ### High-Level Design\n26: \n27: ```\n28: в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n29: в”Ӯ                        AgentCube Platform                                    в”Ӯ\n30: в”Ӯ                                      