{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775895431226,"sessionID":"ses_28468ce19ffebZjIwGuVArSMoW","part":{"id":"prt_d7b9dc2460017Qv32vO8rEOsAr","messageID":"msg_d7b9da41a001KKVh7YZDjkAbST","sessionID":"ses_28468ce19ffebZjIwGuVArSMoW","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_functions.bash:12","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"tail -50 /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/cli/design.md","description":"Check end of design.md"},"output":"| Image removal | <1s | Local operation |\n\n### Optimization Strategies\n\n1. **Layer Caching**: Leverage Docker layer caching for faster rebuilds\n2. **Parallel Operations**: Build/push operations can be parallelized\n3. **Progress Streaming**: Stream logs for better UX on long operations\n4. **Image Pruning**: Cleanup intermediate images to save disk space\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### External Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `docker` | >=6.0.0 | Docker SDK for Python |\n| `requests` | >=2.25.0 | HTTP library (Docker SDK dependency) |\n| `urllib3` | >=1.26.0 | HTTP client (Docker SDK dependency) |\n\n### Python Requirements\n\n```toml\n[project]\ndependencies = [\n    \"docker>=6.0.0\",\n    # ... other deps\n]\n```\n\n---\n\n## Future Enhancements\n\n1. **BuildKit Support**: Use BuildKit for advanced build features\n2. **Multi-platform Builds**: Support for cross-platform image builds\n3. **Build Cache Export**: Export/import build cache for CI/CD\n4. **Image Scanning**: Integration with vulnerability scanners\n5. **Parallel Builds**: Build multiple images concurrently\n6. **Build Metrics**: Detailed timing and resource usage metrics\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- [cli-toolkit/design.md](../../cli-toolkit/design.md) - Overall CLI design\n- [cli-toolkit/spec.md](../../cli-toolkit/spec.md) - CLI specification\n- [Docker SDK for Python](https://docker-py.readthedocs.io/) - Official SDK docs\n- [Docker Engine API](https://docs.docker.com/engine/api/) - REST API reference\n","metadata":{"output":"| Image removal | <1s | Local operation |\n\n### Optimization Strategies\n\n1. **Layer Caching**: Leverage Docker layer caching for faster rebuilds\n2. **Parallel Operations**: Build/push operations can be parallelized\n3. **Progress Streaming**: Stream logs for better UX on long operations\n4. **Image Pruning**: Cleanup intermediate images to save disk space\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### External Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `docker` | >=6.0.0 | Docker SDK for Python |\n| `requests` | >=2.25.0 | HTTP library (Docker SDK dependency) |\n| `urllib3` | >=1.26.0 | HTTP client (Docker SDK dependency) |\n\n### Python Requirements\n\n```toml\n[project]\ndependencies = [\n    \"docker>=6.0.0\",\n    # ... other deps\n]\n```\n\n---\n\n## Future Enhancements\n\n1. **BuildKit Support**: Use BuildKit for advanced build features\n2. **Multi-platform Builds**: Support for cross-platform image builds\n3. **Build Cache Export**: Export/import build cache for CI/CD\n4. **Image Scanning**: Integration with vulnerability scanners\n5. **Parallel Builds**: Build multiple images concurrently\n6. **Build Metrics**: Detailed timing and resource usage metrics\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- [cli-toolkit/design.md](../../cli-toolkit/design.md) - Overall CLI design\n- [cli-toolkit/spec.md](../../cli-toolkit/spec.md) - CLI specification\n- [Docker SDK for Python](https://docker-py.readthedocs.io/) - Official SDK docs\n- [Docker Engine API](https://docs.docker.com/engine/api/) - REST API reference\n","exit":0,"description":"Check end of design.md","truncated":false},"title":"Check end of design.md","time":{"start":1775895431211,"end":1775895431224}}}}
