{"type":"text","timestamp":1775895452736,"sessionID":"ses_28468ce19ffebZjIwGuVArSMoW","part":{"id":"prt_d7b9df9f00019emB1s7xfjzqxr","messageID":"msg_d7b9dc865001JIbKd1d3Jow1XC","sessionID":"ses_28468ce19ffebZjIwGuVArSMoW","type":"text","text":"I have successfully created the `design.md` file for **AR-024: DockerService Encapsulation** in `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/cli/design.md`.\n\n## Summary\n\nThe document (838 lines) includes:\n\n### Architecture\n- Component diagram showing the DockerService layer between CLI commands and Docker Engine API\n- Data flow descriptions for build, push, and remove operations\n\n### Implementation Details\nComplete `DockerService` class with all methods:\n- `check_docker_available()` - Docker daemon health check\n- `build_image()` - Build images with streaming logs and build args\n- `get_image_info()` / `_get_image_info()` - Image inspection\n- `_format_size()` - Human-readable size formatting\n- `push_image()` - Registry push with authentication\n- `_docker_login_sdk()` - Registry login helper\n- `_tag_image_sdk()` - Image tagging helper\n- `remove_image()` - Non-blocking image cleanup\n\n### Integration Examples\n- `BuildRuntime` using DockerService for local builds\n- `PublishRuntime` using DockerService for image preparation\n\n### Other Sections\n- **Data Models** - Build/push result schemas\n- **Error Handling** - Exception types and handling patterns\n- **Configuration** - Environment variables (DOCKER_HOST, proxies)\n- **Testing Strategy** - Unit tests with mock examples\n- **Security Considerations** - Credential handling and image security\n- **Performance Characteristics** - Operation durations and optimizations\n- **Dependencies** - `docker>=6.0.0` SDK\n- **Future Enhancements** - BuildKit, multi-platform builds, scanning","time":{"start":1775895452732,"end":1775895452732}}}
